{
  "title": "Confirmation of an AtoN Light",
  "parse": {
    "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The following terms are used when considering the conspicuity of <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"86c503aa342041d004aad7deccd8e003\">AtoN</span> lights at night.\n</p>\n<table>\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Term</th>\n<th>Definition\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Detection of an <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"86c503aa342041d004aad7deccd8e003\">AtoN</span> light:</td>\n<td>The observer is aware of a light\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Recognition of an <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"86c503aa342041d004aad7deccd8e003\">AtoN</span> light:</td>\n<td>The observer is aware that the light is an <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"86c503aa342041d004aad7deccd8e003\">AtoN</span> light\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Identification of an <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"86c503aa342041d004aad7deccd8e003\">AtoN</span> light:</td>\n<td>The observer is aware of the exact <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"86c503aa342041d004aad7deccd8e003\">AtoN</span> to which the light belongs\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Confirmation of an <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"86c503aa342041d004aad7deccd8e003\">AtoN</span> light:</td>\n<td>The observer identifies the flash character of the signal once again, to verify\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br>\n</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Source: ENG7, Guideline G1073\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/Codes_on_Alerts_and_Indicators\" title=\"Codes on Alerts and Indicators\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"86c503aa342041d004aad7deccd8e003\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Aid to Navigation\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260615131337\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.031 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.039 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 58/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 733/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 398/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   10.916      1 Template:Languages\n100.00%   10.916      1 -total\n 66.48%    7.257      4 Template:Languages/Lang\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki_iala_dictionary_1_41:pcache:idhash:2991-0!canonical and timestamp 20260615131337 and revision id 9195. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>",
